title: Did Trump Campaign Photoshop ‘Trump 2020’ Hat onto Pix of Reality TV Star?
subtitle: A doctored image shows reality TV star Rykard Jenkins in a "Trump 2020" hat.
author: Dan Evon
vclaim: The Trump campaign digitally altered a photograph of reality TV star Rykard Jenkins to make it appear as if he were wearing a "2020 Trump" hat.
